node.text:
For the Kingsford Vegetarian Grill challenge, I made a Vegetarian Burger with a side of butternut squash fries! This burger is smoky, full of flavor and absolutely delicious! I challenge you to make this and join the Kingsford Grill Challenge to win a YETI® Tundra 35 Hard Cooler! Find more recipes and techniques by visiting Kingsford.com or by going to @kingsford on Instagram. 💯

*Kingsford Grill Challenge*

Enter the Grill Challenge for a chance to win a YETI® Tundra 35 Hard Cooler!

1. Must be following @Kingsford
2. Watch the Grill Challenge, try your own at home
3. Post an image of your creation or any proud grilling moment, tag @Kingsford and make sure to use #KingsfordSweepstakes in your caption

Good luck! All entries must be submitted by August 2, 2021 at 11:59am PST.

This giveaway is in no way sponsored, administered by or associated with Instagram, Inc. or YETI®. U.S. only.

Rules: http://cnvrt.us/kingsford

.
All I can say is that it’s “ABSOLUTELY MONEY 💰”

node.text:
For the Kingsford Vegetarian Grill challenge, I made a Vegetarian Burger with a side of butternut squash fries! This burger is smoky, full of flavor and absolutely delicious! I challenge you to make this and join the Kingsford Grill Challenge to win a YETI® Tundra 35 Hard Cooler! Find more recipes and techniques by visiting Kingsford.com or by going to @kingsford on Instagram. 💯

*Kingsford Grill Challenge*

Enter the Grill Challenge for a chance to win a YETI® Tundra 35 Hard Cooler!

1. Must be following @Kingsford
2. Watch the Grill Challenge, try your own at home
3. Post an image of your creation or any proud grilling moment, tag @Kingsford and make sure to use #KingsfordSweepstakes in your caption

Good luck! All entries must be submitted by August 2, 2021 at 11:59am PST.

This giveaway is in no way sponsored, administered by or associated with Instagram, Inc. or YETI®. U.S. only.

Rules: http://cnvrt.us/kingsford
